sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant KServe as KServe Model Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PostgreSQL as PostgreSQL DB<br/>5432/TCP TLS1.2+
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as TrustyAI Operator
    participant EvalJob as Evaluation Job Pod
    participant HuggingFace as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLFlow as MLFlow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>8000/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 1: Model Inference Monitoring
    User->>KServe: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    KServe->>TrustyAI: POST /inference-data<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>(sidecar integration)
    TrustyAI->>PostgreSQL: INSERT inference payload<br/>Auth: Password
    PostgreSQL-->>TrustyAI: ACK
    TrustyAI-->>KServe: 200 OK
    KServe-->>User: Prediction Response

    Note over User,PostgreSQL: Flow 2: Fairness Metric Calculation
    User->>Route: POST /metrics/spd<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>TrustyAI: Forward request<br/>TLS Edge Termination
    TrustyAI->>PostgreSQL: SELECT inference data<br/>Auth: Password
    PostgreSQL-->>TrustyAI: Dataset
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Calculate Statistical<br/>Parity Difference
    TrustyAI-->>Route: JSON metric result
    Route-->>User: Fairness metric

    Note over User,MLFlow: Flow 3: LLM Evaluation Job
    User->>K8sAPI: POST LMEvalJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>EvalJob: Start Pod
    EvalJob->>HuggingFace: Download LLM model<br/>Auth: Token
    HuggingFace-->>EvalJob: Model artifacts
    EvalJob->>S3: Download evaluation dataset<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    S3-->>EvalJob: Dataset files
    EvalJob->>EvalJob: Run lm-evaluation-harness<br/>benchmarks
    EvalJob->>MLFlow: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs<br/>Track experiment
    MLFlow-->>EvalJob: Run ID
    EvalJob->>EvalHub: POST /api/v1/jobs<br/>Update job status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    EvalHub-->>EvalJob: 200 OK
    EvalJob->>S3: Upload results<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    S3-->>EvalJob: ACK
    EvalJob-->>K8sAPI: Job Complete
